{"tid":189231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（休班警）違反保釋條件欲離港拜山。休班警：唔記得咗","createTime":"2017-04-06T09:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-06T13:45:49.000Z","uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"750958b84155b682aa2935bbba06929ff30853f3","tid":189231,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:39:10.000Z","msg":"休班警去年在黃大仙酒後駕駛，事後認罪被罰款5,000元、停牌半年，而他同時面對的一項沒有第三者保險而使用車輛罪，則基於有同類案件正進行上訴，他獲准保釋等候上訴結果始進行答辯，期間不准離港。惟休班警昨被發現循深圳灣離港，今被柙回法院再訊，他向裁判官解釋指打算離港拜山，忘記了不准離港的條件，遭裁判官質疑他身為警員怎會不知道有關條件。"},{"pid":"c97f7caa25576f3c6c2b54689c9328f4308428f3","tid":189231,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:39:43.000Z","msg":"阿sir拜山唔使你教！"},{"pid":"cf35feaf386ae1bd25e1a8ebf5efaed0e362edea","tid":189231,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:41:53.000Z","msg":"留番拜山先講啦"},{"pid":"1960566e4e8a5f75702fb0dd8b7f87b22a8d2117","tid":189231,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:43:35.000Z","msg":"官對呀蛇黎講算係啲咩姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa85402be7ec003e3cab1ab7168446dede5ec50","tid":189231,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:47:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留番拜山先講啦</blockquote><br />\n山都未拜就收左皮了"},{"pid":"a023c135eb07b5c2f63e7ce126996a3b70c0adcc","tid":189231,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:48:27.000Z","msg":"坐監慢慢記啦"},{"pid":"81033d1ef41a04d8668edb5cce12c2f3babfe623","tid":189231,"uid":26333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-06T09:50:27.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67c8caa4507da77f82be2d3201ba5554752a302","tid":189231,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited